{"word":"G472 - ἀντέχομαι - antéchomai - an-tekh'-om-ahee - Hold fast","slug":"G472","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντέχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>antéchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>an-tekh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hold fast"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - antechomai</b> - <i>an-tekh'-om-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G473\">G473</a> and the middle of <a href=\"#/G2192\">G2192</a>; to <i>hold</i> oneself <i>opposite</i> to, that is, (by implication) <i>adhere to</i>; by extension to <i>care</i> for: - hold fast, hold to, support."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1777\">G1777</a>, <a href=\"#/G2192\">G2192</a>, <a href=\"#/G2722\">G2722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3348\">G3348</a>, <a href=\"#/G3353\">G3353</a>, <a href=\"#/G568\">G568</a>"}]}